<exploration xml:id="warm-cuantosVes-arreglos" xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude"> 

<title>Cuántos ves: Arreglos</title>

<statement>
  <p><line>¿Cuántos ves?</line>
    <line>¿Cómo lo sabes?, ¿qué ves?</line></p>
  <image source="svg-source/tikz-file-148581">
      <shortdescription>Arreglo de dos filas, con cuatro círculos azules en cada fila.</shortdescription>
  </image>
  <image source="svg-source/tikz-file-148582">
      <shortdescription>Arreglo de cuatro filas, con tres círculos azules en cada fila.</shortdescription>
  </image>
  <image source="svg-source/tikz-file-148583">
      <shortdescription>Arreglo de cuatro filas, con cinco círculos azules en cada fila.</shortdescription>
  </image>
</statement>

<solution>
    <p>[+++++++++++++++]</p>
    <ul>
      <li>8: I counted 4 dots in each row and there are 2 rows, which is 8. There were 2 dots in each column and there are 4 columns.</li>
      <li>12: I saw 3 dots in each row and there are 4 rows. I saw 4 dots in each column and there are 3 columns.</li>
      <li>20: I saw two 10-frames and 10 plus 10 is 20. I saw 4 rows of 5, which is 20. I saw 5 columns of 4, which is 20.</li>
    </ul>
  </solution>


